dict.string: Search for draft in inbox with following content
Getting list information from online repo...

-- Applescript method has the advantage of not putting Drafts in front, as well as avoiding URL Encoding, saving a few lines
tell application "Drafts" set draftUUID to make new draft with properties {content:"{query}", tags:{"via Alfred"}} end tell
if ((system attribute "openAfter") is "true") then tell application "Drafts" to activate return draftUUID else return "{query}" end if
Getting list information from online repo...

tell application "Drafts" make new draft with properties {content: "{query}", tags: {"via Alfred"}} end tell
return "{query}"

url="{query}"
title=`curl -s $url | grep -o "<title>[^<]*" | cut -d'>' -f2- | cut -d '|' -f 1 | sed 's/[ \t]*$//'`
echo -n "[""$title""](""$url"")"

tell application "Drafts" make new draft with properties {content: "{query}", tags: {"via Alfred"}} end tell
return "{query}"

tell application "Drafts" make new draft with properties {content: "{query}", tags: {"file hook"}} end tell
return "{query}"

if (system attribute "focusedapp") is "PDF Expert" then tell application "System Events" tell process "PDF Expert" set frontmost to true click menu item "Show in Finder" of menu "File" of menu bar 1 end tell end tell delay 0.2 end if
tell application "Finder" to set sel to selection if ((count sel) > 1) then set firstItem to item 1 of sel return POSIX path of (firstItem as text) else return POSIX path of (sel as text) end if

on alfred_script(q)
tell application "System Events" tell process "Drafts" click menu item "Archive" of menu of menu item "Basic" of menu "Actions" of menu bar 1 end tell end tell
end alfred_script
tell application "System Events" tell process "Drafts" to click menu item "Quick Search" of menu of menu item "Find" of menu "Edit" of menu bar 1 end tell

on alfred_script(q) tell application "System Events" tell process "Drafts" set frontmost to true click menu item "Manage Actions..." of menu "Actions" of menu bar 1 end tell end tell end alfred_script

tell application "Drafts" make new draft with properties {content: "{query}", tags: {"OCR"}} end tell
return "{query}"
